## The 3 Agents

| Agent | Input | Outputs | Set up in |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Agent 1 â€” PRD** | Your rough idea | PRD document | Claude Project 1 |
| **Agent 3 â€” Screen Architecture** | PRD from Agent 1 | Screen inventory, flow map, Figma file plan, governance doc | Claude Project 3 |
| **Agent 2 â€” Design System** | PRD from Agent 1 | Design system spec, tokens.json, README | Claude Project 2 |

*Run Agent 3 before Agent 2 â€” the screen inventory informs which components the design system needs to prioritize.*

---

## How to Set Up Each Agent

1. Go to **claude.ai â†’ Projects â†’ New Project**
2. Name it (e.g. `PRD Agent`, `Screen Architecture Agent`, `Design System Agent`)
3. Click **"Project Instructions"** â†’ paste the full contents of the agent's `.md` file
4. Every new conversation in that project behaves as that agent

